{"tid":1008303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【超級碗】場外創歷史 超級碗首次有男性啦啦隊表演","createTime":"2019-02-04T11:19:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-05T00:07:30.000Z","uid":72009,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8c88c4b0896a9d98e8e5fcb05228f4c5c40154b1","tid":1008303,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:19:15.000Z","msg":"美式足球隊新英倫愛國者周日的第53屆超級碗第六度贏得冠軍，球隊的四分衛布拉迪更協助球隊六度封王前無古人，不過今場比賽場外同樣出現另一項前無古人的紀錄。<br />\n<br />\nQuinton Peron和Napoleon Jinnies是洛杉磯公羊的成員，不過他們都不是負責落場比賽的球員，而是球隊的啦啦隊成員，他們兩個更成為超級碗史上首兩位登場表演的男性啦啦隊。<br />\n<br />\n其實男性啦啦隊員並非甚麼新鮮事，不過NFL在2018球季常規賽和今次超級碗才首次有男性隊員參與表演。Peron賽前接受訪問時就表示，對自己有份在超級碗寫下歷史一頁感到興奮：「我們很高興能夠在超級碗表演，洛杉磯是一個擁有不同文化的地方，我認為我們的啦啦隊的背景非常能夠代表我們的城市。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190204/59223993\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F59223993&d=KChxWXaIVet3ZRtCu1MdJxURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=58ea47dd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190204%2F59223993&h=beffa8e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/realtime/article/20190204/59223993</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190204/large/1549273659_7e65.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190204%2Flarge%2F1549273659_7e65.jpg&h=79e65f0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登基佬流口水"},{"pid":"dd67a73d728c79b8c48e40cd8bcdae796f756104","tid":1008303,"uid":92603,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T11:53:04.000Z","msg":"中場有女睇都可以坐低睇下<br />\n<br />\n男人啦啦隊對觀眾就真係中場廁所位黎"},{"pid":"ea7f879646347b2e5be759a28aa6b277ef074f81","tid":1008303,"uid":47674,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-04T12:08:02.000Z","msg":"兩人ig睇落都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/diu.gif\"